page.title: 03MY LIFE IN KEELBY
page.content: I am a ten year old girl.My name is Marie Wickham.I live in the village of Keelby.The school I go to is Keelby County Primary School.My hobbies are dancing,reading and playing with my pet dog,Holly.I enjoy going on walks to the woods.If I am bored I will read my library book from the local library.I am in the church choir and I go to Guides once a week.I live at 37,Eastfield Road,Keelby,Near Grimbsy South Humberside.My house is detached.It has a tiled roof.In the living room we have got a sofa and two chairs to rest on,a television for entertainment also a sterio for music,a sideboard and a unit for cutlery and two tables,one small one for the computer and a big one for eating at.
